{"tid":735600,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［齊叫春］另一半對我唔上心","createTime":"2018-07-09T15:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T15:31:25.000Z","uid":133901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c496fcaa5ffd945de5b241859ffbb4216a7a80a","tid":735600,"uid":133901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:12:17.000Z","msg":"無論係講既野，或者係我既諗法，甚至理想中拍拖既觀念，佢都係用緊佢自己既一套黎套用落我身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都知道其實一直以黎我想要佢做既野，都係將自己果一套強加落佢身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我都只不過係想有名有份，最起馬我送比佢既野或者關心佢既一字一句都可以出現係佢ig story到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他人關心佢同講既野佢都可以cap低之後post係佢自己story到表示自己有人關心好開心，但係我果啲就從來冇出現過，我都唔知我既關心同講過既野其實佢係點諗同有冇上過心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫春完畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1c9b11ccc3528ccc3eca71bbafd1869f1635b6","tid":735600,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa709825ba80f5476b434adca4161a6ce98a1293","tid":735600,"uid":133901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac1c9b11ccc3528ccc3eca71bbafd1869f1635b6","tid":735600,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜我原來咁唔值得佢為左我而付出咩"},{"pid":"50a5b2a57e1a1f6f6fc59126c3864aeb68ecba91","tid":735600,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/231732_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F231732_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=694ae4a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7df25f72edfa22d872440d26b421b65df86e058b","tid":735600,"uid":133901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"同佢唔止一次討論過呢啲問題，不過每當講親呢啲話題既時候，就淨係一句：「好攰」「唔想再講呢啲」就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多時候我都讓步讓左好多，而家甚至連交都廢事鬧，因為鬧完既結果都係一樣，佢都係唔會作出任何改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472d40e2f84829a91d87b1a42b7879e530224864","tid":735600,"uid":133901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}